Bismillah - Once Upon A Time In Mumbaai Dobaara - Akshay Kumar, Imran, Sonakshi

Check out new Eid song "Bismillah" from movie Once Upon A Time In Mumbaai Dobaara starring Akshay Kumar, Imran Khan, Sonali Bendre and Sonakshi Sinha. 

This final chartbuster from Once Upon A Time In Mumbai Dobaara will surely set the dance floor ablaze. This song is composed and sung by Anupam Amod wjile lyrics are penned by Rajat Aroraa

Song: Bismillah

It is directed by Milan Luthria and produced by Ekta Kapoor and Shobha Kapoor. It is a sequel to the 2010 hit film Once Upon a Time in Mumbaai.
